query: SELECT r.r_name, COUNT(c.c_custkey) AS num_customers FROM customer c JOIN nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey JOIN region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey GROUP BY r.r_name ORDER BY num_customers DESC
SELECT p.p_type, AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS avg_supply_cost FROM part p JOIN partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey GROUP BY p.p_type ORDER BY avg_supply_cost DESC
SELECT s.s_name, SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_avail_qty FROM supplier s JOIN partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey GROUP BY s.s_name ORDER BY total_avail_qty DESC
SELECT o.o_orderpriority, COUNT(o.o_orderkey) AS num_orders FROM orders o WHERE o.o_orderdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY o.o_orderpriority ORDER BY num_orders DESC

SELECT c.c_mktsegment, SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM customer c JOIN orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY c.c_mktsegment ORDER BY revenue DESC

SELECT p.p_brand, COUNT(l.l_orderkey) AS num_orders FROM part p JOIN lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY p.p_brand ORDER BY num_orders DESC

SELECT r.r_name, SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM region r JOIN nation n ON r.r_regionkey = n.n_regionkey JOIN customer c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey JOIN orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY r.r_name ORDER BY revenue DESC

SELECT p.p_container, SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM part p JOIN lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY p.p_container ORDER BY revenue DESC

SELECT s.s_name, SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM supplier s JOIN lineitem l ON s.s_suppkey = l.l_suppkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY s.s_name ORDER BY revenue DESC

SELECT p.p_mfgr, COUNT(l.l_orderkey) AS num_orders FROM part p JOIN lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY p.p_mfgr ORDER BY num_orders DESC

SELECT r.r_name, COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) AS num_suppliers FROM region r JOIN nation n ON r.r_regionkey = n.n_regionkey JOIN supplier s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey GROUP BY r.r_name ORDER BY num_suppliers DESC

SELECT p.p_type, COUNT(DISTINCT l.l_orderkey) AS num_orders FROM part p JOIN lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY p.p_type ORDER BY num_orders DESC

SELECT c.c_mktsegment, COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS num_orders FROM customer c JOIN orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey WHERE o.o_orderdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY c.c_mktsegment ORDER BY num_orders DESC

SELECT r.r_name, COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS num_customers FROM region r JOIN nation n ON r.r_regionkey = n.n_regionkey JOIN customer c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey WHERE c.c_acctbal > 1000 GROUP BY r.r_name ORDER BY num_customers DESC

SELECT p.p_brand, COUNT(DISTINCT l.l_partkey) AS num_parts FROM part p JOIN lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY p.p_brand ORDER BY num_parts DESC

SELECT s.s_name, COUNT(DISTINCT l.l_orderkey) AS num_orders FROM supplier s JOIN lineitem l ON s.s_suppkey = l.l_suppkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY s.s_name ORDER BY num_orders DESC

SELECT r.r_name, AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS avg_acctbal FROM region r JOIN nation n ON r.r_regionkey = n.n_regionkey JOIN customer c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey GROUP BY r.r_name ORDER BY avg_acctbal DESC

SELECT p.p_container, COUNT(DISTINCT l.l_partkey) AS num_parts FROM part p JOIN lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey WHERE l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31' GROUP BY p.p_container ORDER BY num_parts DESC
SELECT s.s_name, AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS avg_supply_cost FROM supplier s JOIN partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey GROUP BY s.s_name ORDER BY avg_supply_cost DESC

SELECT r.r_name, SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_avail_qty FROM region r JOIN nation n ON r.r_regionkey = n.n_regionkey JOIN supplier s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey JOIN partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey GROUP BY r.r_name ORDER BY total_avail_qty DESC
